{
  "stem": "21812.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then, I saw a couple of others.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just a few.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Books, again, when you think about that, books were not readily available.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I loved books.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a, a private library.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember where there were any public ones.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't believe there were, except maybe the university library.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But there were little private libraries.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I used those all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was one-- there were two books that would come out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Like, an encyclopedia came out every year.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One was scientific, and the other one was just travel and general.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was always looking forward to the next issue.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I couldn't wait to, to get those.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And sometimes I would-- a couple of times, I think, my father bought them for me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then, I remember when he was-- he had promised me that he would buy it for me, and, and-- the next one-- because I had done extremely well in school.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was on top of tying for second place, I think.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then, he lost his job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And, and, you know, things were terrible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I never got that book, and I was terribly disappointed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I loved books and always read a lot of books, yeah.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We read all of that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had-- I had an excellent education in gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a marvelous foundation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had almost five years of Latin and all the German writers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] And we read all of those, and the Greek mythology.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was an amazing education for, for-- when you think about it, for a 11-year-old, 10-year-old, 11.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was even younger because I still got into that class.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
